---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Quvii Blog"
  description="How Quvii handles cookies, analytics, and advertising."
>
  <div class="container-page py-14 lg:py-20 max-w-3xl prose-pm">
  <h1 class="text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-body-faint">Last updated: 2026-05-14</p>

  <div class="prose-pm max-w-prose">
    <p>
      This page covers the editorial blog hosted at
      <code>quvii.com/blog</code>. For the Quvii product
      (account creation, billing, image generation, team management),
      please see the main
      <a href="https://quvii.com/privacy">Quvii Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>What this blog collects</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics 4 records page
        views, referrer, device type, and approximate geolocation
        (city / region). Data is aggregated and used to understand
        which articles are useful — never to identify individuals.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Advertising:</strong> the blog displays Google AdSense
        ads. AdSense uses cookies to serve relevant ads. Manage your
        choices via the on-page consent banner (Google-certified CMP),
        Google's
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Ads Settings</a>,
        or
        <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">aboutads.info</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>UTM parameters:</strong> when you click a link from this
        blog to the Quvii product (e.g. signup CTAs), we attach
        UTM parameters so the product team can attribute conversions
        to specific articles. These do not contain personal data.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>No accounts on the blog.</strong> The blog has no
        login. Product accounts are created on
        <a href="https://quvii.com">quvii.com</a> and that
        flow has its own privacy disclosure.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      A Google-certified Consent Management Platform asks you to
      Consent / Manage / Decline on your first visit. AdSense and GA4
      set cookies according to your choice. Clear cookies for
      <code>quvii.com</code> to revisit the prompt.
    </p>

    <h2>Removing your data</h2>
    <p>
      Analytics data is aggregated and not individually keyed; we
      cannot delete specific page views. For any other request, email
      <a href="mailto:editor@quvii.com">editor@quvii.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Google Analytics —
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener" target="_blank">privacy policy</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Google AdSense —
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="noopener" target="_blank">ads policy</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Cloudflare — hosting and CDN. See
        <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Cloudflare privacy</a>.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
